{"article_id":"1ym7LkI2WwgsmDwF","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Republican efforts","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"to find a replacement for President Obama 's healthcare system","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"have collapsed .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"Two Republican senators said","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"they opposed their party 's proposed alternative ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"making it impossible for the bill to pass in its current form .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"The party has been divided on the issue ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"with moderates concerned about the effects on the most vulnerable .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"President Trump has now called for repeal of Obamacare ,","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"so Republicans can start `` from a clean slate '' .","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"`` Regretfully , it is now apparent that the effort","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"to repeal and immediately replace the failure of Obamacare","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"will not be successful , ''","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"Mr McConnell said .","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"President Trump had made repealing and replacing Obamacare ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"under which more than 20 million people gained healthcare coverage ,","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"a key campaign pledge .","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"Republicans view the 2010 legislation as an overreach of the federal government","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"and say","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"patients have less choice and higher premiums .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"The party 's proposed alternative had kept key Obamacare taxes on the wealthy ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"while imposing sharp cuts to healthcare for the poor","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"and allowing insurers to offer less coverage .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"Two Republican senators , Mike Lee and Jerry Moran , said","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"the new legislation did not go far enough","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"in repealing Obamacare .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"Mr Moran said","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"`` we should not put our stamp of approval on bad policy ''","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"while for Mr Lee ,","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"`` in addition to not repealing all of the Obamacare taxes","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"[ the bill ] does n't go far enough","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"in lowering premiums for middle class families ;","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"nor does it create enough free space from the most costly Obamacare regulations '' .","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"Two senators","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"- Rand Paul and Susan Collins -","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"had already opposed the bill .","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"Mr Paul said","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"the bill kept too much of the `` ObamaCare taxes '' ,","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"while Ms Collins expressed concerns about cuts to Medicaid .","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"With the two new opponents , Republicans","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"- who hold 52 seats -","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"no longer have enough votes","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"to pass the bill in the 100-member Senate .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"Moderate Republicans had also said","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"the bill would have harmed some of their vulnerable constituents .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"The non-partisan Congressional Budgetary Office","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"( CBO )","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"found","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"the bill would have stripped 22 million Americans of health insurance over the next decade .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"On top of that , polls had shown","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"Obamacare remained popular among Americans","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"-","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"a survey by the Washington Post and ABC News on Monday found","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"more than twice as many people preferred Mr Obama 's programme to the proposed alternative .","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"In the end the death blow to the latest iteration of Obamacare repeal came from the right flank .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"Mr McConnell was always going to have to walk a fine line in his effort","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"to keep both moderates and hard-core conservatives in party on board with his healthcare reform proposal .","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"After his first draft failed to garner sufficient support ,","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"he came out with a new version","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"that moved farther to the right in key areas","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"while throwing money","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"to keep the moderates satiated .","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"That strategy worked in the House ,","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"where Freedom Caucus arch-conservatives and just enough moderates came around","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"to rescue the legislation from death 's doorstep .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"This time the entire rickety structure came tumbling down .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"The Senate may very well try to vote on straight-up repeal ,","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"as the president has suggested","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"- one with a two-year fuse -","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"but it faces long odds","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"in winning a majority support .","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"If and when that fails ,","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"it 's back to the drawing board for Republicans .","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"This is n't the end of congressional efforts","depth":4},{"id":74,"text":"to pass healthcare legislation .","depth":4},{"id":75,"text":"But it 's likely the end of the repeal-and-replace war","depth":4},{"id":76,"text":"as it 's been waged for the past six months .","depth":4},{"id":77,"text":"Mr Trump urged Republicans to repeal the `` failing Obamacare now","depth":5},{"id":78,"text":"and work on a new healthcare plan","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"that will start from a clean slate '' .","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"Mr McConnell said","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"he would try to pass a repeal of Obamacare with a two-year delay implementation","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"that would provide a `` stable transition period '' to a new legislation .","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"Correspondents , however , say","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"that this plan has little chance","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"of passing","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"as , under the interim period , millions would be left without healthcare .","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"Republican Senator John McCain ,","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"who is recovering from surgery ,","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"called for a bipartisan strategy","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"to produce a new bill .","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"`` The Congress must now return to regular order ,","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"hold hearings ,","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"receive input from members of both parties , ''","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"he said in a statement .","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"Democrats have said","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"they will not co-operate to repeal Obamacare ,","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"but that they can work in a bipartisan way","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"to improve it .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"Senate Democratic Leader Charles Schumer said on Twitter :","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"`` This second failure of Trumpcare is proof positive","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"that the core of this bill is unworkable . ''","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":203,"left":174,"right":202,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":174,"left":115,"right":173,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":109,"right":114,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":104,"right":108,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":103,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":103,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"